<br>
If the opportunity costs of playing EQ after the price increase is too much, your money is better spent elsewhere.  Since you will no long be playing EQ, your opinion, from the perspective of the company, does not matter as you are a &quot;have not&quot;.<br>
<br>
This concludes the first chapter of Microeconomics 101. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=8078.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=8078.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.showPrevMessage?topicID=8078.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.showNextMessage?topicID=8078.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8078.topic&index=50><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=8078.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.threadControl?topicID=8078.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8078.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fnamelesstaverngeneraldiscussion.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8078.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><ta